Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.decorators

Class StandardPower

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.decorators.StandardPower
All Implemented Interfaces:
Power
public class StandardPower
extends java.lang.Object
implements Power
StandardPower represents the standard power that all gods have in common. maxMoves and maxBuild can't be changed once StandardPower has been created.

      public boolean endOfTurn​(java.util.ArrayList<Worker> workers)
      This method is called when a player finish his turn. It checks that player has done standard moves and reset all counters or flag for the turn in model.
      Specified by:
      endOfTurn in interface Power
